snippet.textDisplay:
My favourite childhood song being musically reprised with a great fusion of Flamenco guitars & Jazz brass section. Ritu Raj & Nandita's voice - just awesome.
However the female harmony with Ritu Raj's vocals is not working. Their tonal quality is too high, almost a shrill. Pink Floyd are a great example of using female harmony with male vocals.

snippet.textDisplay:
বাগিচায় বুলবুলি তুই ফুলশাখাতে
দিসনে আজি দোল ।
আজো তার ফুলকলিদের ঘুম টুটেনি
তন্দ্রাতে বিলোল ।।

আজো হায় রিক্ত শাখায় উত্তরী বায়
ঝুরছে নিশিদিন
আসেনি দখনে হাওয়া গজল গাওয়া
মৌমাছি বিভোল ।।

কবে সে ফুল-কুমারী ঘোমটা চিরি
আসবে বাহিরে ,
শিশিরের স্পর্শসুখে ভাঙবে রে ঘুম
রাঙবে রে কপোল ।।

ফাগুনের মুকুল – জাগা দুকুল ভাঙ্গা
আসবে ফুলের বান ,
কুড়িদের ওষ্ঠপুটে লুটবে হাসি ,
ফুটবে গালে টোল ।।

কবি তুই গন্ধে ভুলে ডুবলি জ্বলে
কুল পেলিনে আর
ফুলে তোর বুক ভরেছিস আজকে জলে
ভরবে আখির কোল ।।

snippet.textDisplay:
Ufffff awesome outstanding ever best song heard heard in my lifetime. Salute to whole team!!! 

First our national poet nothing new! To me he is most underrated but greatest poet in the world! Why ? Look at his magic of playing with words, music, lyrics, compassion, composition and depth of feelings and expressions and rhythms - wow - bilol, dol, bivol, kopol, etc - simply mesmerizing, outstanding!!!!! I’m blown away!!!! How a 100 years old song can be so modern touchy mind boggling!!!!! Look at English translation even better than original Bengali lyrics that would beat any English poetic masterpiece!!! Wow! Genius of nazrul so amazing amusing and mesmerizing!!!!

Dear Arnob- you just composed best ever song in history! Keep up your best work buddy! Literature art doesn’t have boundary - you can win the world in this digital age. I’m listening it sitting in America. Salute!

Dear guitarist- you blew whole world off!!! Ever best guitar heard!

Dear saxophonist- simply mind boggling!!!!!

Dear all musicians- all superb even clapping was outstanding!

Dear Ritu - sorry with due regards today you beat the great Manabendro!!! You may rock the world! Your classical voice, perfect pronunciations awesome, ornamental sweet voice even rhythmic charismatic body language - superb. Plz keep up your good work. You can reach the peak buddy!

Dear Nandita - hardly I heard you before but you mesmerized me with your addictive voice even with your rhythmic body language.

I used to feel down why we can’t have great music listening to other coke studios as we have quantitatively and qualitatively great literature, culture and outstanding poets. You all fulfilled me with just one song.

Plz plz plz explore our all great literature culture poets from Tagore nazrul lalon Hasan raja shah Karim and many other talents. Plz do remember it’s always one of the greatest soft power to win across globe. Yes you have done and you can do very best InshaAllah. Salute or you all young Turks . March ahead and conquer the world BH greatest Bengali music!!!
